# File Structure

## Key Files
- [src/js/components/App.js](mdc:src/js/components/App.js) - Main application logic and state management
- [src/js/services/youtubeApi.js](mdc:src/js/services/youtubeApi.js) - YouTube API integration  
- [src/js/services/analytics.js](mdc:src/js/services/analytics.js) - Data analysis processing
